        "text": "Information Technology",
        "title": "Critical Infrastructure Sectors",
        "category": "other"
      },
      {
        "text": "The DeepAI.org endpoint `https://api.deepai.org/change_user_email` accepts POST requests without any CSRF protection. If a logged-in user is tricked into visiting a malicious HTML page, an attacker can change the user's email address to their own and take over the account via password reset.",
        "title": "Risk Evaluation",
        "category": "summary"
      },
      {
        "text": "Fixed May 20, 2026.",
        "title": "Recommended Practices",
        "category": "general"
      },
      {
        "text": "United States",
        "title": "Company Headquarters Location",
        "category": "other"
      }
